Package: pi-adc-control
Version: 2.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Roasted-Codes
Depends: python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, i2c-tools
Description: Apple Studio Display 17" CRT control for Raspberry Pi
 Power on/off, geometry calibration, and brightness control for the
 Apple Studio Display 17" CRT (M7768) via a Jason ADC adapter.
 Uses USB HID for monitor control and DDC/CI over GPIO for power.
